commit_message:
Move patching logic to separate place

Add 4 patching hooks:
- pre node;
- pre deploy;
- post deploy;
- post node.

Also:
- remove separate hooks related to patching;
- add tests.

Change-Id: Id46ffd7ccbcbc8b56a21a126e0a9f55cc6192e27
Related-Bug: #1372988
